text":"Therefore said he unto them, The harvest truly is great, but the labourers are few: pray ye therefore the Lord of the harvest, that he would send forth labourers into his harvest.","year":32},{"id":"recqDeNHiOGrkeUla","ref":"Luke.10.3","text":"Go your ways: behold, I send you forth as lambs among wolves.","year":32},{"id":"recJTP3cDMq75N4m8","ref":"Luke.10.4","text":"Carry neither purse, nor scrip, nor shoes: and salute no man by the way.","year":32},{"id":"recXFKKzKj8TbhBR3","ref":"Luke.10.5","text":"And into whatsoever house ye enter, first say, Peace be to this house.","year":32},{"id":"recMyWpgADVRiRI6c","ref":"Luke.10.6","text":"And if the son of peace be there, your peace shall rest upon it: if not, it shall turn to you again.","year":32},{"id":"recWOaf2imLLtQxnx","ref":"Luke.10.7","text":"And in the same house remain, eating and drinking such things as they give: for the labourer is worthy of his hire. Go not from house to house.","year":32},{"id":"recMqU9fljU52EIRi","ref":"Luke.10.8","text":"And into whatsoever city ye enter, and they receive you, eat such things as are set before you:","year":32}]}
